text: Kyzyl-Barzhau () is a rural locality (a village) in Novokulevsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 55 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Krasnaya Gorka, 11 km from Novokulevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Kyzyl-Barzhau
